00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,000
[SPEAKER_03] ali nismo izgubli vjeru.

219
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:58,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja ću se vratiti na...

220
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,000
[SPEAKER_03] Kad je bilo prekviće,

221
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,000
[SPEAKER_03] Frada Stjepane?

222
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:05,000
[SPEAKER_03] Kad vam je Blaženi Aliziv Stepinac,

223
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:07,000
