228
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:25,000
[SPEAKER_03] I eto, to je sve za sada.

229
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:28,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja se nadam da nisam bio dosadan,

230
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:30,000
[SPEAKER_03] ali eto, to je...

231
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_03] Želim vam svako dobro

232
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,000
[SPEAKER_03] i Bog vas plakoslovi.

233
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:47,000
[SPEAKER_02] Dobar veče, ja sam Luka,

234
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:51,000
