235
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:56,000
[SPEAKER_02] i isto tako, ja imam svoje turnire,

236
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_02] i želim bih čuti,

237
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:00,000
