255
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] i tako sam ja radio, pa eto.

256
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ima tamo jedno pitanje,

257
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja ću jedno postaviti isto.

258
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene zanima,

259
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] pratim ovako nekad,

260
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,000
