261
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] nego samo pratim sportaše

262
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] i vidim da ponekad da

263
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:13,000
