272
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,000
[SPEAKER_03] gdje sam,

273
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:45,000
[SPEAKER_03] gdje sam bio jako nesiguran nakon ozljede

274
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:49,000
[SPEAKER_03] i kad sam ozdravio, počeo sam pomalo igrati,

275
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,000
[SPEAKER_03] pa sam razmišljao,

276
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:53,000
[SPEAKER_03] znači zagrijavanje,

277
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] kako sam se zagrio,

278
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:58,000
[SPEAKER_03] jesmo pobjedili ovaj tjedan,

279
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,000
[SPEAKER_03] jesmo,

280
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,000
[SPEAKER_03] e drugi tjedan ću tako isto se zagridu.

281
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:03,000
[SPEAKER_03] Međutim,

282
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,000
[SPEAKER_03] normalno,

283
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,000
[SPEAKER_03] to nije,

284
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,000
[SPEAKER_03] to nema veze sa vjerom.

285
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:12,000
[SPEAKER_03] Kogod je prazna vjeran,

286
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:15,000
[SPEAKER_03] to vam ja pričam i opet iz svog iskustva,

287
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:19,000
[SPEAKER_03] samo znak nesigurnosti u sebi

288
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,000
[SPEAKER_03] i ono što radiš.

289
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:22,000
[SPEAKER_03] I eto,

290
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:24,000
[SPEAKER_03] to je bila jedna kratka faza,

291
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,000
[SPEAKER_03] što se mene događalo,

292
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:27,000
[SPEAKER_03] međutim,

293
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:28,000
[SPEAKER_03] eto,

294
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:30,000
[SPEAKER_03] vidio sam, naučio sam

295
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:32,000
[SPEAKER_03] i ovaj,

296
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,000
[SPEAKER_03] te stvari,

297
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,000
[SPEAKER_03] ja kad to isto vidim,

298
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,000
[SPEAKER_03] meni je,

299
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,000
[SPEAKER_03] ja uvijek kažem,

300
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,000
[SPEAKER_03] vjerujem u Boga,

301
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,000
[SPEAKER_03] a ovo drugo,

302
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:41,000
[SPEAKER_03] ne treba se ništa bojati,

303
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:45,000
[SPEAKER_03] ako neko vjeruje da će tri puta skakat na jednu nogu,

304
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,000
[SPEAKER_03] ili ne znam šta,

305
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] da je to donese nekome sreću,

306
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:50,000
[SPEAKER_03] nažalost,

307
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,000
[SPEAKER_03] mene to osobno,

308
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,000
[SPEAKER_03] nije ne osuđujem nikoga,

309
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:55,000
[SPEAKER_03] ali to mene samo pokazuje da je ta osoba jako nesigurna.

310
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,000
[SPEAKER_03] Eto.

311
00:21:56,000 --> 00:22:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dolešer,

312
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] moj ime Mario.

313
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Po vama se vidi da imate iskustvo životnog i crkvenog.

314
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se još tražim.

315
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ste bili ljuti na Boga kad ste izgubili čer?

316
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, teško pitanje, ali,

317
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] da li ste bili ljuti na Boga kad ste izgubili dijete?

318
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je ovdje još neko blizu ko će postati pitanje da ja ne bavim se sportom cijelu večer ovdje.

319
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:53,000
[SPEAKER_03] ovako,

320
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:58,000
[SPEAKER_03] ja ne mogu biti ljutna na drago me Bogu.

321
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:02,000
[SPEAKER_03] Nije moj čer preminila,

322
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:06,000
[SPEAKER_03] dragi Bog je meni dao moj čer,

323
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:09,000
[SPEAKER_03] a dragi Bog je uzeo moj čer.

324
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:19,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja sam zahvaljen drago me Bogu šta je dragi Bog meni dao snagu da ja ovdje mogu danas s vama pričati od nju.

325
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_03] Opet!

326
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:35,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja sam imao priču sa različiti ljudi koji su imali slično iskustvo gdje je djet prminilo.

327
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:42,000
[SPEAKER_03] I možda je to tako meni moralo se dogoditi da ja to vidim.

328
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:46,000
[SPEAKER_03] I ti ljudi, neki određeni su bili ljuti na drago me Bogu.

329
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:54,000
[SPEAKER_03] Šta ja osobno, pa neću reći, ja sam ne slažem, sigurno svatim, ali i razumijem.

330
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:58,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ali to je opet faza gdje nismo svi isti.

331
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:00,000
[SPEAKER_03] Svak tugo je drugačiji.

332
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:06,000
[SPEAKER_03] I mene je osobno jedino jedino pomoglo.

333
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:11,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja sam ti jednu skoro godinu danas svaki večer molio Krunicu

334
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:17,000
[SPEAKER_03] i kroz moljene Krunicu sam dobio snagu za ići dalje.

335
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:25,000
[SPEAKER_03] Snagu za, eto, niko neće vratiti na ovom svijetu moj čer.

336
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:34,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ali ima, ima i, ja imam utjeha koliko toliko, koliko god vam to nekako čudno zvuči.

337
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:38,000
[SPEAKER_03] Ja znam da je moj čer odšla u raj.

338
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:50,000
[SPEAKER_03] Moje djete, ona je uvijek će biti moje djete i ona je odšla sto posto u raj i to je meni osobno da je utjeha.

339
00:24:50,000 --> 00:25:02,000
[SPEAKER_03] Sad je do mene da ja jedan dan kad ja preminem, da sam ja zaslužio ići gore kod nju, biti kod nju i to je meni još jedna dodatna motivacija.

340
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:12,000
[SPEAKER_03] Hvala što pratite.

